title: BRIEF-I3D signs 370,530 zloty net deal
text:
BRIEF-I3D signs 370,530 zloty net deal Sept 28 
Sept 28 I3D SA : 
* Signs 370,530 zloty ($97,588) net deal for delivery of interactive stations to Centrum Nauki Leonardo da Vinci in Podzamcze, Poland Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7969 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
